\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 She sat thinking about it for what seemed a long time, then nodded herself and got up with the pages in her hand. 'I'll go out back,' she said. 'The sun is very warm this morning.'\par
